### Создание новых записей (POST)
POST http://localhost:8080/persons/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": {
    "name": "Ann",
    "surname": "Doe",
    "age": 25
  },
  "phoneNumber": "+1234567890",
  "city": "New York"
}

